GCP lets you build and host apps and websites, store data, and analyze data on Google's scalable infrastructure.

## <a id='prereqs'></a>Prerequisites

To integrate GCP as a single sign-on identity provider for <%= vars.app_runtime_abbr %> apps,
you must have the following:

* A <%= vars.product_short %> service plan with **Plan Administrators** and **Organizations** configured. See [Manage Service Plans](../manage-service-plans.html).
* An active Google Cloud project.
* A GCP user account with project editor or higher privileges.

